  "overview": {
    "welcome_summary": {
      "en": "Welcome to the Faculty of Veterinary Medicine, ECU’s faculty for animal health, public veterinary hygiene, food safety, and veterinary clinical training.",
      "ar": "مرحباً بك في كلية الطب البيطري، كلية ECU لصحة الحيوان والصحة العامة البيطرية وسلامة الغذاء والتدريب الإكلينيكي البيطري.",
      "source_url": "https://ecu.edu.eg/faculties/veterinary-medicine/"
    },
    "description": {
      "en": "The faculty offers a B.V.Sc. route with five academic years, one year of field training, six specialisation programmes, and eight scientific departments.",
